    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270460/extras/84a800814bec3b9365f44b1f71d232bf.avif?t=1762958902\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270460/extras_big/84a800814bec3b9365f44b1f71d232bf.webp?t=1762958902 width=1560 height=610 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>该冲向香蕉了</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款香蕉VR平台跳跃游戏中，你将扮演一只会杂技的猩猩，在太空攀岩架上自由摇摆和抛掷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你已经坠落在一个云雾缭绕的星球上，需要收集香蕉来给你的飞船加油。在9个充满活力的云端生物群落中闯荡75个游戏关卡，步步晋级为TOSS!??大师吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款VR游戏，包含了只有在经典平台游戏才能体验到的敏捷性、跳跃时机和玩家技巧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐵 跑酷动作：在空中翱翔和发射自己，抓住树木、管道和墙壁。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 挑战：试着与时间赛跑，完成时间挑战；在每一轮中找到香蕉越多越好，进行抓取越少越好。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍌 社区挑战：互相比拼名次和所耗时间，跟上你朋友的排行榜幽灵。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥋 熟练度和修改器： 成为TOSS!??大师，解锁诸如零重力和双重抛掷的修改器吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270460/extras/dec4b46c7054001ca8e714bd8d19d2ca.avif?t=1762958902\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270460/extras_big/dec4b46c7054001ca8e714bd8d19d2ca.webp?t=1762958902 width=1560 height=506 /></span></p>",
